  "instructions": [
    "Heat 1 tablespoon of ghee or avocado oil in a large Dutch oven over medium heat.",
    "Add the diced onion and cook until it starts to brown, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for another minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add the sliced ginger and cook for 1-2 minutes, until it starts to soften.",
    "Add the chicken and cook until it is browned on all sides, about 5-7 minutes.",
    "Add the chili flakes, cumin, coriander, smoked paprika, and salt. Stir to combine.",
    "Add the diced tomatoes and bring the mixture to a boil.",
    "Cover the pot and transfer it to the preheated oven.",
    "Bake for 30 minutes, or until the chicken is cooked through and the sauce has thickened.",
    "Garnish with chopped parsley and serve hot."
  ],
